PrecisDesignation of PAMELA MARGARET ELIZABETH WILLIAMSON of Northeastern Manitoulin and The Islands, Ontario, a member of the National Seniors Council, to be Chairperson of the National Seniors Council, to hold office during pleasure for a term ending on April 11, 2027, effective July 1, 2024.
